WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.760
Those who are new,
please come in front.

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:25.180
Already you have been told
about Sahaja Yoga.

00:00:25.180 --> 00:00:28.480
Sahaja Yoga&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:34.840
is nothing modern;
it's not a modern invention.

00:00:38.360 --> 00:00:46.600
It is the culmination
of the living force

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:49.240
that is working in you,
the living process,

00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:57.880
the evolutionary process
which took place spontaneously.

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:07.800
This force that has made you
into human beings,

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:12.080
and the same force is going
to work on somebody more.

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:26.280
So, all other things that we expect
to do about our union with God,

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:31.960
union with our Spirit,
is of no use,

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:39.800
because it has to be spontaneous;
it has to be done

00:01:39.800 --> 00:01:49.600
by the living force within us.
Whatever we do is by will.

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:57.520
They are artificial.

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:06.840
So, to change ourself from within,
not from without,

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:13.560
something has to happen
within ourselves.

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:16.880
Because our attention is outside,
we can change our dress as we like.

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:20.040
We can have the kind of chair
that we want to have.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:23.080
We can have the kind of house
we want to live in.

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:25.440
We can have the garden
we want to have.

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:31.480
But we cannot transform the inside.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:39.360
That has to happen by some force
already based within us,

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:41.320
which is to be activated.

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:46.440
Unless and until this living
actualisation takes place,

00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:51.320
whatever else happens to us
is outside.

00:02:56.120 --> 00:02:57.920
When we say we try
to change ourselves,

00:03:00.920 --> 00:03:02.880
we cannot go too far.

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:08.440
What we see is how we react,
how we behave,

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:12.800
how we talk to others.

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:17.880
At the most, we might be able
to see how we are sensitive.

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:22.360
Some people are very sensitive,
some are insensitive.

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:27.800
Some are hot-tempered,
some can wait patiently.

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:33.120
Some appear to be truthful.
Some are very lunatic.

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:38.120
Some are dynamic, some are lazy.
But this is all outside.

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:48.080
All these expressions coming
outside are manifesting,

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:54.640
coming from some sort of
a natural thing within us.

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:59.920
Unless and until we transform
those natural things within us,

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:04.120
whatever we do outside
is just superficial.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:08.120
Like a tree has some sort
of a disease,

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.440
or you find some leaves are rotten.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:21.000
Even if you remove those things,
no use treating the tree

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:24.600
from the leaves.
You have to treat it from the root.

00:04:27.760 --> 00:04:34.200
In the same way, within you,
the roots are subtle.

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:35.560
And how to approach those roots?

00:04:36.640 --> 00:04:39.720
Those roots are the subtle
centres in you.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:47.880
I hope they have explained to you
these centres which are with us.

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:52.280
You find it very difficult to believe
that there are these centres.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:55.280
There are many people who have
never heard about them,

00:04:56.720 --> 00:05:00.160
and many who have never heard
about the force,

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:03.320
that power within us by which
we give&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:09.560
expression

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:13.240
to our Self, to our Spirit.

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.960
Nobody has seen it
and nobody knows what it is.

00:05:18.960 --> 00:05:21.400
Some people have written about it,
some say things about it,

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:26.280
but we cannot believe it.
It's not easy to believe.

00:05:27.480 --> 00:05:34.200
It sounds bombastic, maybe
just some sort of a myth.

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:43.431
But if the tree has to manifest,
we have to go to the roots.

00:05:43.431 --> 00:05:43.600
Now, how do we do this?

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:49.560
Many people say,
"I look into myself".

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:53.600
How do you do this?
How far can you go?

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:56.880
You cannot even go
to your subconscious.

00:05:59.600 --> 00:06:00.960
How can you go
to your unconscious?

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:04.480
If you could go
to your unconscious,

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.880
it would not be called
an 'unconscious' — it's conscious.

00:06:08.640 --> 00:06:11.160
So your conscious mind cannot go
up to the unconscious.

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:17.480
At the most, you may go
to the subconscious area,

00:06:17.480 --> 00:06:22.760
some hallucination or something,
and then come back to the same.

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:35.160
Like a person who wears
blue glasses

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:38.120
sees everything blue
and then gets confused.

00:06:40.320 --> 00:06:42.840
There is no transformation
that has taken place in the eyes.

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:48.240
And the others just say,
"Only a little colour change".

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:56.200
And that is not to be accepted
as something real.

00:06:57.320 --> 00:06:59.280
Because if it is real,
it doesn't change.

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:03.000
You are a human being;
it's a reality.

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:05.065
If you suddenly change
like a monkey becomes,

00:07:05.065 --> 00:07:08.560
and then again you become
a human being,

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:11.840
then your state as a human being
is not a reality, just a dream.

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:13.920
Maybe a monkey is dreaming
he is a human being,

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:18.680
or a human being is dreaming
he is a monkey.

00:07:19.760 --> 00:07:21.640
It's just a dream.
There is no reality about it.

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:28.400
In the same way, if we have
to take ourselves inside,

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:32.440
we have to see ourself inside,
we have to take our attention inside.

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.080
And how do we do it?

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:39.720
To know if there are any centres,
to know if there are any roots,

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:47.080
to know that all the manifestations
have taken place within us,

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:49.320
or even to know if what I am
saying is true or not,

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:52.960
first your attention
has to go inside.

00:07:54.320 --> 00:07:57.720
It has to go.
I don't have to lecture you,

00:07:57.720 --> 00:08:04.480
"Take your attention inside".
It's not like that.

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:10.513
It's not in your control.
It's not your doing;

00:08:10.513 --> 00:08:11.640
it's a fact,
one must accept it.

00:08:15.760 --> 00:08:17.040
How does the attention work?&nbsp;

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:21.880
Till the attention is outward,

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:23.960
it's all on the surface.

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:27.680
How do we take the attention inside?

00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:32.320
If there is such an idea in the mind,
that shows your attention is outside.

00:08:33.560 --> 00:08:37.720
But it can be taken inside;
not by you,

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:44.120
but by that living force within us
that has made us human beings.

00:08:48.800 --> 00:08:51.480
Something has to happen
in our consciousness.

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:56.230
Something has to happen.
Otherwise, we are not going to

00:08:56.230 --> 00:09:01.160
believe it. Animals are not bothered;
they don't want to believe in it.

00:09:02.520 --> 00:09:03.240
They just exist.

00:09:04.400 --> 00:09:06.080
But you want to believe
in something,

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:10.720
to see for yourself.
You want to have the proof of it.

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:15.200
That's why something has to happen
to you as a human being,

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.520
that you believe it
and you see it for yourself.

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:24.760
And this happening only takes place
among the human beings.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:30.480
When a fish became a reptile,
he did not have to feel it;

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:33.840
he just became.
The fish is not bothered.

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.560
It has to happen
in your consciousness.

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:47.360
And to happen, something has to
happen within.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:52.200
And that happening is called
Kundalini awakening,

00:09:53.160 --> 00:09:54.640
the awakening of this power.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:10:00.004
That is the power
that has to rise within you.

00:10:00.004 --> 00:10:00.920
It is placed in
the triangular bone.

00:10:02.280 --> 00:10:03.396
You can actually see
with your naked eyes

00:10:03.396 --> 00:10:05.456
the pulsation of the Kundalini.

00:10:05.456 --> 00:10:07.960
In many people,
you can actually see it.

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.880
You can also feel the pulsation
rising.

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:12.160
You can also feel it
on top of your head.

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:22.560
Then the pulsation stops,
and you are amazed

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:23.560
that suddenly you become
completely silent.

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:32.240
There is no thought
and you start feeling inside-out.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:37.360
You start feeling your centres
on your fingers.

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:43.720
First, you start feeling
the cool breeze coming through you.

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:52.800
Then you start feeling the centres
that are enlightened,

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:54.800
meaning there are subtle centres
enlightened within us.

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.851
If your problem is
on the emotional side,

00:10:58.851 --> 00:10:58.878
you'll feel it on the left.

00:10:58.878 --> 00:10:59.240
If they are on the physical
and the mental side,

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:01.760
you feel it on the right.

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:06.120
Different centres have
a lot to reveal;

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:08.960
you start feeling them.

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:13.120
Many people don't know
how one can change.

00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:17.720
Even after 42 days, some struggle.

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:20.911
And I said,
"You are in a bad shape".

00:11:20.911 --> 00:11:22.928
He said, "What's the matter?"

00:11:22.928 --> 00:11:28.640
I said, "You have got
a very bad liver".

00:11:28.640 --> 00:11:31.480
I said, "You have got
a lot of heat because of the spleen".

00:11:31.480 --> 00:11:36.040
"Yes. I have got spleen cancer.
How do you know?"

00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:48.440
"I can feel it."

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:06.160
Because I can see myself inside,
I can see in your heart.

00:12:06.160 --> 00:12:09.120
Because you can see yourself
in the mirror,

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:11.080
you can see others also.

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:14.080
If you cannot see yourself
in the mirror, you are blind.

00:12:16.520 --> 00:12:20.880
That's the first thing one notices —
that you are blind.

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:26.840
When you cannot see
yourself inside,

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:27.252
you cannot see others inside.

00:12:27.252 --> 00:12:27.440
And not to feel them
on your fingertips.

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:34.040
And that is why one has to jump
into a new awareness.

00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:37.440
A new awareness of a new dimension,

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:43.240
by which you see yourselves inside
and you see others also,

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:48.200
by which you just record
what's wrong with them.

00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:52.600
You do not hate or love,
but you know what is wrong.

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:54.720
Actually, you feel them
within yourself.

00:12:55.800 --> 00:12:57.760
What could be a greater love
than that?

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:01.320
"Love thy neighbour as thyself."

00:13:01.320 --> 00:13:04.760
You just become the other person,
just like that.

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:09.160
A very happy feeling.

00:13:10.480 --> 00:13:13.440
Then only you realize
that something new has happened.

00:13:15.560 --> 00:13:17.760
Realization these days
is very easy.

00:13:19.400 --> 00:13:20.680
It has started working well.

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:32.000
I had to work very hard
in the beginning.

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:34.320
But once it clicked,
now it's much better.

00:13:35.760 --> 00:13:39.240
It's very easy,
but there are two things about it.

00:13:40.920 --> 00:13:44.000
First is that people don't come
for Realisation.

00:13:58.920 --> 00:14:00.560
They are seekers,
born as seekers.

00:14:02.040 --> 00:14:05.200
Now, those who are seeking
are also enamoured

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:13.200
by something that is just
with their ego,

00:14:13.200 --> 00:14:14.880
in which people say,
"You can do something,

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:18.760
you can stand on your head
and jump on your feet,

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:19.320
and you can get it".

00:14:20.080 --> 00:14:22.040
But here we say,
"No, nothing of the kind.

00:14:22.040 --> 00:14:28.288
Something has to happen within.
You just can't do anything about it."

00:14:28.288 --> 00:14:32.200
"It's too much" —
that somebody has to help you.

00:14:41.920 --> 00:14:44.960
It's too much for the ego to accept
that somebody else is going to help.

00:14:49.400 --> 00:14:58.240
Or otherwise, it is the superego —
they can just mesmerize,

00:14:58.240 --> 00:14:58.560
absolutely mesmerize.

00:14:58.560 --> 00:15:00.080
And with mesmerism,
people do all kinds of things.

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.200
Here there is complete freedom.

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.320
If you want to have Realization,
you can have it.

00:15:05.320 --> 00:15:06.600
If you don't want to,
then not.

00:15:07.280 --> 00:15:09.040
Even after having it,
if you want to use it,

00:15:09.560 --> 00:15:12.640
you are welcome.
Nobody is going to force

00:15:12.640 --> 00:15:16.880
Realization on you.
That's your own acceptance

00:15:17.480 --> 00:15:25.155
and your own choice.
Otherwise, it doesn't work out.

00:15:25.155 --> 00:15:27.040
It cannot go further,
it just stops.

00:15:27.040 --> 00:15:40.320
That is why it is a thing
chosen by you earnestly.

00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:43.560
Here, Sahaja Yoga doesn't run
after you;

00:15:43.560 --> 00:15:49.800
you have to run
after Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:50.640
It doesn't take any money.

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:56.120
How can it?
You cannot pay for God.

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.400
You cannot pay for the Divine.

00:15:58.400 --> 00:15:59.920
You cannot purchase God
or sell Him.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:07.600
It's a living process.
It's your blessing already given.

00:16:09.520 --> 00:16:10.560
It's within.

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:25.480
You cannot do anything for it,
I can.

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:26.800
So anybody can say,
"You stand on your head,

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:32.040
you will do it."
But maybe I may say,

00:16:32.040 --> 00:16:32.455
"It doesn't work out."

00:16:32.455 --> 00:16:34.080
You start thinking
in the third person —

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:40.840
"It doesn't work out.
Now what is it?"

00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:44.600
"It works out or it does not
work out."

00:16:44.600 --> 00:16:46.800
For example, my own daughter came
on earth without Realization.

00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:53.880
It's not necessarily because
she is my daughter

00:16:53.880 --> 00:16:58.600
that she should get Realization.

00:17:01.000 --> 00:17:05.720
It's your own.
It's your own bank account

00:17:06.600 --> 00:17:08.880
that is free.
It is yours.

00:17:13.400 --> 00:17:17.930
It is not that you have to judge,
but you are to be judged.

00:17:17.930 --> 00:17:29.000
That's so precious,
so wonderful.

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:32.840
The Divine forgives.
It is so great.

00:17:35.600 --> 00:17:39.440
God Almighty has already decided
that we have to save this creation,

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:47.120
and the creation is
the human being.

00:18:01.080 --> 00:18:02.600
He should save.
He can't afford to destroy it.

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:12.077
And that's how it is —
as if a computer has been put

00:18:12.077 --> 00:18:13.160
to the mains.

00:18:14.040 --> 00:18:17.000
You start wondering what dynamics
are based in all of you.

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:24.960
You start understanding
the Divine laws and Divine times,

00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:29.560
and how your body was specially made
for such a thing as this.

00:18:29.560 --> 00:18:31.840
And once you get connected
through yoga,

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:34.360
the whole dynamism starts flowing,

00:18:36.360 --> 00:18:43.760
and how every action and
every thought, every word

00:18:45.240 --> 00:18:46.080
has a meaning for you.

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:54.360
It is really fantastic
and can happen to anyone,

00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:56.080
and it has to happen.

00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:04.827
I'm sure you all
are going to feel it.

00:19:06.880 --> 00:19:11.440
But I have to tell you
that there is no way

00:19:11.440 --> 00:19:12.360
one can bind you.

00:19:13.760 --> 00:19:16.840
It is only your own desire —
the pure desire

00:19:16.840 --> 00:19:19.000
to become the Self
is the Kundalini.

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:25.292
And if you have that pure desire
really in you,

00:19:25.292 --> 00:19:26.440
it is going to work out.

00:19:26.440 --> 00:19:30.200
There is no way one can bind you.
There is no membership,

00:19:31.760 --> 00:19:34.040
no enrolment, nothing like that.

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:44.280
There is no contract, no force,
nothing!

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:50.800
So it is you who has to accept it
in your own choice,

00:19:50.800 --> 00:19:51.600
in your own freedom.

00:19:54.680 --> 00:19:56.960
Nobody can force it
down anybody.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:05.320
And that's why one has to understand
that one has to accept

00:20:05.320 --> 00:20:10.080
this thing of Self.

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:15.440
And you know I am here because
I feel that Self,

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:19.480
I feel that spark within Me.
That is why I am here.

00:20:20.520 --> 00:20:23.720
You may not believe Me,
but I know it.

00:20:24.920 --> 00:20:28.000
I'm here just to give you
what is yours,

00:20:29.080 --> 00:20:32.800
what belongs to you.
That's all.

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:40.960
I don't want anything.
I can't take things.

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:49.520
The only thing that I can give
is the subtle spark.

00:20:52.720 --> 00:20:54.840
Nothing more, nothing less.

00:20:59.280 --> 00:21:01.840
I'm sure it is going to work out.

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:39.200
It started in London with
six people,

00:21:49.720 --> 00:21:51.635
and for four years,
I worked with six people.

00:21:51.635 --> 00:21:56.316
From these six people,
gradually it grew.

00:21:56.316 --> 00:22:04.040
One has to get it,
establish it within you,

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:11.960
rise above.
And you will be amazed

00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:13.440
how wonderful it is.

00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:21.869
For the first time, I'm in this area.
It's a beautiful area, I must say.

00:22:21.869 --> 00:22:24.840
But still, people don't think
of the beauty that resides within.

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:29.440
They don't think of the peace
that they have within them.

00:22:30.640 --> 00:22:32.920
They don't want to seek.
They are going to the Moon.

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.520
When are they going to go
to their Spirit?

00:22:37.360 --> 00:22:41.640
They talk of it, they read about it;
it's a fashion to talk of this.

00:22:42.520 --> 00:22:45.557
But I wonder how they use
their mind.

00:22:45.557 --> 00:22:47.240
If they were, they would come
